<html>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: small">
<table border=0>
<tr valign=top><td>Pan:</td><td><ul><li>Left mouse button click & drag - all directions<li>Left/Right/Up/Down arrows on the keyboard<li>Left mouse button click once to center view</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Zoom:</td><td><ul><li>Use the scroll wheel on the mouse<li>Plus (+) and Minus (-) on the keyboard<li>Left/Right mouse button double click to zoom in/out and center</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Tilt:</td><td><ul><li>Right mouse button click & drag - up and down<li>Page Up and Page Down on the keyboard<li>Hold Ctrl on the keyboard and Left mouse button click & drag - up and down<li>Hold Shift and Up/Down arrows on the keyboard</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Rotate:</td><td><ul><li>Right mouse button click & drag - left and right<li>Hold Ctrl on the keyboard and Left mouse button click & drag - left and right<li>Hold Shift and Left/Right arrows on the keyboard</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Stop:</td><td><ul><li>Spacebar</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Reset heading:</td><td><ul><li>N</ul></td></tr>
<tr valign=top><td>Reset all:</td><td><ul><li>R</ul></td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
